{
  "id": "69a3ae470e552b4448478a26",
  "title": "HTML の入れ子構造のルール",
  "created": 1772334665,
  "updated": 1772350838,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a3ae470e552b4448478a26",
      "text": "HTML の入れ子構造のルール",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772334665,
      "updated": 1772334665
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3ae48000000000070b945",
      "text": "HTMLの文法的に合法であっても、コンテンツカテゴリーの観点から[入れ子構造]に制約が与えられることがある。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772334665,
      "updated": 1772350808
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3ae6d000000000070b947",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772334702,
      "updated": 1772334702
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3ae7b000000000070b948",
      "text": "Wikipedia の「Lint エラー: タグの入れ子構造の誤り」として発生するエラーの原因。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772334716,
      "updated": 1772334753
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3aea1000000000070b94b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772334753,
      "updated": 1772334753
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3aea1000000000070b94c",
      "text": "[https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Guides/Content_categories コンテンツカテゴリー - HTML | MDN]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772334754,
      "updated": 1772334764
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3aeac000000000070b94e",
      "text": "> [https://gyazo.com/d650088eb6787aa3cafe4a6eaf60305e]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772334765,
      "updated": 1772334833
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3aeeb000000000070b94f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772334828,
      "updated": 1772334828
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3ae4d000000000070b946",
      "text": "この図の[包含関係]って、集合としての包含関係 (inclusion) なのだろうか？",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772334670,
      "updated": 1772350827
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b1cc000000000070b9b1",
      "text": "\t埋め込み [$ \\sub]記述[$ \\sub]フロー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772335565,
      "updated": 1772335622
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b217000000000070b9b2",
      "text": "\t見出し[$ \\sub]フロー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772335639,
      "updated": 1772335645
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b21d000000000070b9b3",
      "text": "\t区分[$ \\sub]フロー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772335647,
      "updated": 1772335650
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b4dc000000000070b9b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336349,
      "updated": 1772336350
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b1b0000000000070b9b0",
      "text": "それとも [component] として中に含める (composite) ことができるのだろうか？",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772335537,
      "updated": 1772350838
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6fb000000000070b9c8",
      "text": "\tcode:こんなふうに.html",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336892,
      "updated": 1772336902
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6af000000000070b9be",
      "text": " \t<フロー>",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336816,
      "updated": 1772336912
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6e6000000000070b9c6",
      "text": " \t\t<見出し></見出し>",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336871,
      "updated": 1772336929
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6e7000000000070b9c7",
      "text": " \t\t<区分></区分>",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336871,
      "updated": 1772336928
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6d7000000000070b9c5",
      "text": "  \t<記述>",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336856,
      "updated": 1772336915
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6c0000000000070b9c4",
      "text": "  \t\t<埋め込み></埋め込み>",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336833,
      "updated": 1772336947
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6bc000000000070b9c1",
      "text": "  \t</記述>",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336828,
      "updated": 1772336919
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6b3000000000070b9c0",
      "text": " \t</フロー>",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336820,
      "updated": 1772336955
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b6a4000000000070b9bd",
      "text": " [https://www.tohoho-web.com/html/memo/html5.htm#category HTML5 - とほほのWWW入門]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336804,
      "updated": 1772336816
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b595000000000070b9ba",
      "text": "  とほほが一番情報がうまくまとまっている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336534,
      "updated": 1772336796
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b687000000000070b9bc",
      "text": "  \tinclusion と composition を区別している。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336776,
      "updated": 1772336796
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3b5a4000000000070b9bb",
      "text": "\t\tてかHTMLの中に ruby ([Ruby.icon]) 入れられるのか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772336549,
      "updated": 1772337784
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3ba0c0000000000fefbb0",
      "text": "\t\t\tちがう。Ruby ([Ruby.icon]) ーじゃなくて[$ \\overset{ルビ}{これ}]か",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772337677,
      "updated": 1772337806
    },
    {
      "id": "69a3bb600000000000324401",
      "text": "\t\t\t[ルビ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772338016,
      "updated": 1772338022
    },
